channel.title: Looking for testers: Nalifornia (637) Testers (Build: January 15, 2016)
channel.description:
Hello there,
I'm the founder and developer of Nalifornia. I really need some game testers, opinions and ideas are really valuable to me and the others.
If you want to help out by testing out the game, around 9.00 PM (GMT +2) (3.00 PM Central American Time) We'll launch the game for testers only.
If you'd like to know more check out my website:
- https://nalifornia.com
[IMG]https://nalifornia.com/community/uploads/images/1452639776_Bar%20Fight.jpg[/img]
If you're interested, let me know below, in the comment section. :)
After you let me know, I will send you a PM with further info. I appreciate it a lot! :)
[I]Thanks for reading[/I],
- Nalifornia
